        {
            "title": "外滙基金大豐收 余偉文憂三風險  去年賺3310億新高 各類資產錄正回報",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"外滙基金大豐收 余偉文憂三風險 去年賺3310億新高 各類資產錄正回報\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"504\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GJzeJsz3SmIQxOwAl9YHHA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/75ab8850-fca3-11f0-b7fd-c0f60b1485a8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">外滙基金大豐收 余偉文憂三風險 去年賺3310億新高 各類資產錄正回報</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
